Effective Date: 21 january 2023

Thank you for using SASO! This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.

1. Information We Do Not Collect:

We want to be clear that we do not collect any personal data or personally identifiable information (PII) from our users. This includes, but is not limited to, your name, email address, phone number, location, or any other sensitive information.

2. Device Information:

While using our app, we may collect certain non-personal information related to your device. This may include the type of device you use, the device's unique identifier, the operating system, and other technical information. However, this information is used solely for the purpose of improving the performance and functionality of our app and is not linked to any personally identifiable information.

3. Cookies and Tracking:

We do not use cookies or any tracking mechanisms to collect information about your online activities across different websites or apps.

4. Third-Party Services:

Our app does not integrate with any third-party services that would require the sharing of user data. We do not have access to any data collected by third-party services.

5. Children's Privacy:

Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect any personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and become aware that your child has provided us with any information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes to our information practices. We encourage you to periodically review this page for the latest information on our privacy practices.

7. Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices or this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

By using our app, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Thank you for trusting SASO!

